{"tid":2268770,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邏輯推理小測驗(思方網)","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T16:24:36.000Z","uid":373794,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b822bde99c234948d1f63b015b8c881f32f75a49","tid":2268770,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"資料來源：<a href=\"https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/quiz-validity.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hku.hk%2Fthink%2Fchi%2Fquiz-validity.php&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=32a66f1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hku.hk/think/chi/quiz-validity.php</a> 思方網<br />\n平日見到唔少人講野個陣時，唔太著重對話內容嘅推演邏輯，所以搞出咗好多笑話，自己聽完可能會當普通野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，內心笑過就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n但係當發覺到愈來愈多人都係咁樣嘅時候，就不得不正視呢種現象。<br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲基本嘅邏輯學，例子所描述嘅既定事實唔適用於現實，因為宜家只係理論課程，未去到應用層面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2inXsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2inXsx.jpg&h=bdeee9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVH0Kav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVH0Kav.jpg&h=664c9305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多嘅問題，都可以用<span class=\"red\">畫圈圈</span>整理邏輯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/687jZL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F687jZL0.jpg&h=9a472140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/je83G4k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fje83G4k.jpg&h=391fd42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要識得分幾時用 <span class=\"gold\">OR</span> 幾時用 <span class=\"red\">AND</span>。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z7rprx2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz7rprx2.jpg&h=5f901b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2anW19g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2anW19g.jpg&h=83087686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意程度字眼(<span class=\"red\">所有</span>，<span class=\"green\">大部份</span>，<span class=\"blue\">小部份</span>，<span class=\"green\">沒有</span>........)"},{"pid":"c78d132cedf4833b5577f1f7495e52227caa201f","tid":2268770,"uid":373794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/effd4pA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feffd4pA.jpg&h=a0385fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家思考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca04537e7428c1aa8df8c898a5102d1d5e474ce","tid":2268770,"uid":93060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"答案正確。10 題問題你已答了 10 題，總共答對了 10 題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eca9f2253bdf04622a5820e49d3aea788011da8","tid":2268770,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5ca04537e7428c1aa8df8c898a5102d1d5e474ce","tid":2268770,"uid":93060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"答案正確。10 題問題你已答了 10 題，總共答對了 10 題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"答案不正確。10 題問題你已答了 10 題，總共答對了 0 題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4b70d182596b0ea2acd90f103c13b6844912e0","tid":2268770,"uid":279606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img s